since we don't need scaffold-only tests anymore. I’m considering if I can delete it using bash commands like `rm`. But to be safe, I might create a new TypedAnnotationWriterTest.java file instead. I also need to ensure that my new class is correctly titled and placed within the appropriate package.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying annotation behavior**\\n\\nI'm thinking about how the boolean value being set to true impacts the TypedAnnotationWriter. If the default is true and we call true, it seems like TypedAnnotationWriter would skip adding that member. I realize I can’t set a default for all annotations to assert—they should be handled individually, especially since the annotation method itself doesn’t have a default value. I need to be careful about how defaults interact with the annotations I’m working with.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_2U7izKtfr7mXwb75hbyHM53L|fc_04cdc765ca541aa90169f7712a74c48197aaf05719599b806d", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.glassfish.jaxb/codemodel/4.0.6/src/test/java/org_glassfish_jaxb/codemodel/TypedAnnotationWriterTest.java", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_glassfish_jaxb.codemodel;\n\nimport com.sun.codemodel.JAnnotationUse;\nimport com.sun.codemodel.JAnnotationWriter;\nimport com.sun.codemodel.JCodeModel;\nimport com.sun.codemodel.JDefinedClass;\nimport com.sun.codemodel.JFormatter;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\nimport java.io.StringWriter;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\n\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\n\npublic class TypedAnnotationWriterTest {\n    @Test\n    void typedAnnotationWriterCreatesProxyAndDispatchesAnnotationMembers() throws Exception {\n        JCodeModel codeModel = new JCodeModel();\n        JDefinedClass generatedType = codeModel._class(\"example.GeneratedType\");\n\n        CodeLabelWriter writer = generatedType.annotate2(CodeLabelWriter.class);\n        CodeLabelWriter chainedWriter = writer.label(\"primary\").enabled(true).priority(7).type(String.class);\n\n        assertThat(chainedWriter).isSameAs(writer);\n        assertThat(writer.getAnnotationType()).isEqualTo(CodeLabel.class);\n\n        JAnnotationUse annotationUse = writer.getAnnotationUse();\n        assertThat(annotationUse.getAnnotationClass().fullName()).isEqualTo(CodeLabel.class.getName());\n        assertThat(annotationUse.getAnnotationMembers()).containsOnlyKeys(\"label\", \"enabled\", \"priority\", \"type\");\n\n        String renderedAnnotation = render(annotationUse);\n        assertThat(renderedAnnotation)\n                .contains(\"label=\\\"primary\\\"\")\n                .contains(\"enabled=true\")\n                .contains(\"priority=7\")\n                .contains(\"type=String.class\");\n    }\n\n    private static String render(JAnnotationUse annotationUse) {\n        StringWriter out = new StringWriter();\n        JFormatter formatter = new JFormatter(out);\n        annotationUse.generate(formatter);\n        formatter.close();\n        return out.toString();\n    }\n\n    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n    public @interface CodeLabel {\n        String label();\n\n        boolean enabled();\n\n        int priority();\n\n        Class<?> type();\n    }\n\n    public interface CodeLabelWriter extends JAnnotationWriter<CodeLabel> {\n        @Override\n        JAnnotationUse getAnnotationUse();\n\n        @Override\n        Class<CodeLabel> getAnnotationType();\n\n        CodeLabelWriter label(String value);\n\n        CodeLabelWriter enabled(boolean value);\n\n        CodeLabelWriter priority(int value);\n\n        CodeLabelWriter type(Class<?> value);\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 562, "output": 1213, "cacheRead": 35328, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37103, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777824028169, "responseId": "resp_04cdc765ca541aa90169f7711ca1e48197bd266a5405df8f26"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_2U7izKtfr7mXwb75hbyHM53L|fc_04cdc765ca541aa90169f7712a74c48197aaf05719599b806d", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2668 bytes to tests/src/org.glassfish.jaxb/codemodel/4.0.6/src/test/java/org_glassfish_jaxb/codemodel/TypedAnnotationWriterTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777824046801}]}
